rted: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThere are ending statements that never deprive one who said them: glorifying Allah thirty-three times after every prayer, praising Him thirty-three times, and exalting Him thirty four-times.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Nasa\u0304'i\u0304 1350 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25238,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/10\/04\/salat-al-duha-four-rakaat\/","url_meta":{"origin":32771,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Prayer: Four cycles of Salat al-Duha","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 4, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Darda reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAllah Almighty said: Son of Adam, bow to Me in four cycles of prayer\u00a0at the beginning of the day and I will suffice you for the rest of it.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 475 Grade: Sahih (authentic)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24471,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/03\/05\/dua-takbir-tasbih-before-asking\/","url_meta":{"origin":32771,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Exalt, glorify, praise Allah before asking","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 5, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: Umm Sulaym came to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and she said, \u201cTeach me some words to say in my prayer.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cExalt Allah ten times, glorify Allah ten times, praise Allah ten times, then ask for whatever you wish. Allah\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":13527,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/04\/11\/virtue-fajr-jamaah-jumuah\/","url_meta":{"origin":32771,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Fajr: Dawn prayer in congregation on Friday","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 11, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, the best of prayers to Allah is the dawn prayer in congregation on Friday.\u201d Source: Shu\u2019ab al-Ima\u0304n 2790 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u064e \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18133,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/02\/16\/every-bidah-is-misguidance-fire\/","url_meta":{"origin":32771,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Bid&#8217;ah: Every innovation is misguidance in Hellfire","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 16, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir ibn 'Abdillah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would praise Allah in his sermon, as He deserves to be praised, and then say, \u201cWhomever Allah guides, no one can lead him astray. Whomever Allah sends astray, no one can guide him. The truest word\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/32771","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=32771"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/32771\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=32771"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=32771"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=32771"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}